value.name: 125.4 – Seikaku Technical Group Limited
value.snippet: Description. Specifications. Download. The 125.4 is a Class-H switching power amplifier dedicated to fixed installations. It features four independent 125 W channels driving both 4 Ω loads and 70 V/100 V lines. Unlike most of 100 V amplifiers, the 125.4 does not use any output transformer, so the signal fed to the speakers is pure and natural.
